<% title "Perks for #{@event.name}" %>
<% page_md %>
<%= render 'events/nav' %>

<h1>
  Promotions &amp; perks
</h1>

<div class="card pb0 mb3" id="pvsa">
  <div class="card__banner card__banner--top flex justify-between items-center promo-pvsa">
    <%= image_tag 'https://cloud-q7i8htyv7-hack-club-bot.vercel.app/0pvsa-logo-2x.png', width: 60 %>
    <%= link_to 'Purchase',
      organizer_signed_in? ? "https://hack.af/pvsa-order?prefill_Event%20Name=#{@event.name}&prefill_Submitter%20Email=#{current_user.email}" : root_path,
      class: "btn mr1 #{'disabled' unless organizer_signed_in?}"
    %>
  </div>

  <p>
    Since you run on Hack Club Bank, you can issue <a href="https://www.presidentialserviceawards.gov" target="_blank">Presidential Volunteer Service Awards</a> to volunteers (including to yourself and team members).
    While applying you'll be asked to provide evidence for the submitted volunteer hours (instructions and examples are provided on the application form).
  </p>

  <p>
    While Hack Club Bank is registered with PVSA as a certifying organization and will submit rewards on your behalf, the costs charged by PVSA for certificates and medals will come from your own budget.
    Certificates and medals are shipped to one address and you'll distribute them from there.
  </p>

  <h3 class="mb0 mt0">PVSA Cost Summary</h3>
  <p class="italic muted mt0 mb0">All costs are from PVSA directlyâ€”we don't charge you a fee on top.</p>
  <table class="mb2">
    <tr>
      <td>Certificate only</td>
      <td>$5.00</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Certificate + Pin</td>
      <td>$6.50</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Certificate + Coin</td>
      <td>$10.50</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Certificate + Medallion</td>
      <td>$10.50</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Shipping (per order)</td>
      <td>Varies (up to $23.00)</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <section class="card__banner card__darker secondary border-top">
  <p class="my0">
    Only ðŸ‡ºðŸ‡¸ US citizens and LPRs who currently reside within the US are eligible to recieve the award. You can see all the <a href="https://www.presidentialserviceawards.gov/eligibility#volunteers" target="_blank">volunteer eligibility details</a> if you have any questions.
  </p>
  </section>
</div>

<div class="card mb3" id="domains">
  <div
    class="card__banner card__banner--top flex justify-between items-center promo-domains">
    <h3 class="h1 p2 my0 color-black">Domains</h3>
    <%= link_to 'Apply',
      organizer_signed_in? ? "https://hack.af/bank-domains?prefill_Project%20Name=#{@event.name}&prefill_Bank%20URL=#{event_url(@event)}&prefill_Name=#{current_user.full_name}&prefill_Login%20email=#{current_user.email}" : root_path,
      class: "btn bg-success mr1 #{'disabled' unless organizer_signed_in?}"
    %>
  </div>

  <p class="mb0">
  Running a high school student-led hackathon, nonprofit, or club? Hack Club Bank will purchase your domain for under $20 and cover the cost for the first year. After the first year you'll be responsible for paying to renew. You'll also have the option of setting up <%= link_to 'Google Workspace', event_g_suite_overview_path %> once we've purchased your domain.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="card mb3" id="replit">
  <div
    class="card__banner card__banner--top flex justify-between items-center"
    style="background-color: #0d101e; border: 1px solid #0068ad;">
    <%= image_tag 'replit.png', width: 170 %>
    <%= link_to 'Apply',
      organizer_signed_in? ? "https://hack.af/replpromo?prefill_Project%20Name=#{@event.name}&prefill_Bank%20URL=#{event_url(@event)}&prefill_Your%20name=#{current_user.full_name}&prefill_Organizer%20team%20size=#{@event.organizer_positions.size}" : root_path,
      class: "btn bg-success mr1 #{'disabled' unless organizer_signed_in?}"
    %>
  </div>

  <p class="mb0">
    Repl.it is giving <strong>free Hacker Plans</strong> to organizers of all Hack Club Bank projects,
    for 1 year. Repl.it is an amazing web IDE, where you can get basically any programming language
    running in your web browser in just a few secondsâ€”regardless of what kind of computer you have.
    The Hacker plan, normally $84, gives you private projects, unlimited collaborators, & unlimited storage.
  </p>
</div>

